    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it's looking for its next adventure! It's been so reliable for me and is in really solid shape\u2014just a few minor signs of being loved, but it still runs like a total dream. It's perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend road trips. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so you\u2019re getting a fantastic, reliable ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the sought-after 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. Crucial enthusiast maintenance has been addressed, including professional rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive Vanos system overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The chassis remains composed with upgraded Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain delivers linear power and visceral induction noise. A performance-first specimen for the serious driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. Regular maintenance recorded. No mechanical issues. $29,500 firm.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
